Package org.eclipse.m2m.atl.drivers.emf4atl

Class EMFModelLoader

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.m2m.atl.engine.vm.ModelLoader
org.eclipse.m2m.atl.drivers.emf4atl.EMFModelLoader
Direct Known Subclasses:
UMLModelLoader
public class EMFModelLoader extends ModelLoader
Loads EMF models into a ResourceSet. Make sure to use the same model loader for all EMF models used in a model transformation! Use different model loaders for different threads.
